Package: gsa.gov
Title: General Services Administration API Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for GSA APIs. Access federal per diem travel
    rates, City Pair airfares, Site Scanning data for federal websites, and the
    GSA open data catalog. All functions return tibbles.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: httr2, jsonlite, dplyr, tibble
